# TITLE
# Begin with a capitalized verb,  use the imperative mood, do not end with a period
# |<----  Using a Maximum Of 50 Characters  ---->|
# If applied, this commit will ...

# Separate subject from body with a blank line

# BODY
# Explain what and why this change is being made (not how)
# Tell a story
# Can use multiple lines with "-" for bullet points in body
# |<----   Try To Limit Each Line to a Maximum Of 72 Characters   ---->|
# Why is this change needed? (Prior to this change, ...)

# How does it address the issue? (This change ...)

# FOOTER
# Provide links or keys to any relevant tickets, articles or other resources

# COMMIT END

